query:
UPDATE software_licenses SET
            client_id = $2, name = $3, vendor = $4, version = $5,
            license_key = $6, license_type = $7, seats = $8, used_seats = $9,
            purchase_date = $10, expiry_date = $11, renewal_date = $12,
            cost = $13, notes = $14, updated_at = NOW()
        WHERE id = $1
